Package com.amplifyframework.devmenu

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DeveloperMenu.HideAction
    Interface to handle the action to take when the developer menu should be hidden.
    ShakeDetector.Listener
    Interface to handle shake events when they occur.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DeveloperMenu
    Manage the display and shake detection behavior for the developer menu.
    DeveloperMenuActivity
    This is the activity to display the developer menu.
    DeviceInfo
    Contains information about the Android device currently running the application.
    DevMenuDeviceFragment
    A Fragment subclass representing the view to display the device information on the developer menu.
    DevMenuEnvironmentFragment
    A Fragment subclass representing the view to display the environment information on the developer menu.
    DevMenuFileIssueFragment
    A Fragment subclass corresponding to the file issue view for the developer menu.
    DevMenuLogsFragment
    A Fragment subclass representing the view to display the logs on the developer menu.
    DevMenuMainFragment
    A Fragment subclass representing the main view for the developer menu.
    EnvironmentInfo
    Contains information about the plugin versions added to the application and the developer's environment.
    LogEntry
    A representation of a log.
    PersistentLogStoragePlugin
    Implementation of the LoggingCategoryBehavior that stores logs.
    ShakeDetector
    Detects a device shake event.
